
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MY Usta OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        table {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff5733;
        }
        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center;">
                <h1>MY Usta OTP Verification</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <p>Dear User,</p>
                <p>Your OTP for verification is:</p>
                <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p>
                <p>Please use this OTP to complete your verification process. This OTP is valid for a limited time.</p>
                <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
                <p>Best Regards,<br>The MY Usta Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
